It depends on the aspect ratio of the movie. 1280x720 is 16/9, but many movies are shot in a "wider" ratio, hence the black borders on top & bottom of your TV screen.
You can have a look here for further information : http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aspect_ratio_%28image%29

